## Architecture

```
Browser (HTML/JS)
  │
  ├─ Image upload  ──────────────────────────────► Cloud Storage
  │
  └─ WebSocket (audio stream + session ID)
         │
         ▼
   Cloud Run (FastAPI)
         │
         ├─ Gemini Live API  ◄──── (audio in, audio out + JSON structured output)
         │        │
         │        └─ Annotation updates → sent to browser via WS
         │
         └─ Gemini Vision API  ◄── (image analysis on upload)
                  │
                  └─ Initial annotation JSON → sent to browser
```

